<section>
  <p>Economists in the Government Economic Service (GES) don’t just analyse figures. They’re closely involved in helping to shape government policy.</p>

  <p>The GES is the UK’s largest recruiter of economists, with over 1,400 professionals involved in all aspects of government policy. They work in more than 30 departments and agencies.</p>

  <p>Joining the GES as a Fast Stream economist can give you a wide range of career options. It also allows you to make an impact on life in the UK and beyond.</p>

